Joseph J. DEMTY, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1102, 3D17-1101 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017

ORDERED that appellant's notice of voluntary dismissal is recognized by the Court, and these consolidated appeals from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida are hereby dismissed.
